---
import CenterPageBanner from "./shared/CenterPageBanner.astro";

const items = [
  {
    title: "Minimal Distractions",
    description:
      "Avoid autoplay** videos, pop-ups, or flickering elements. Limit animation or make it easy to pause/disable. Use clean layouts with generous whitespace. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Clear Visual Hierarchy",
    description:
      "Use **bold headings**, **short paragraphs**, and **bullet points** to chunk information.Highlight key actions (e.g. buttons, forms) clearly with contrast and spacing.Consistent layout and predictable placement of elements.",
  },
  {
    title: "Simple, Intuitive Navigation",
    description:
      " Use a **sticky nav bar** or breadcrumb trail.Keep navigation labels clear and concise (e.g., “Work” instead of “Our Portfolio of Past Collaborations”). Avoid hiding important links in drop-downs or hamburger menus unless necessary.",
  },
  {
    title: " Focus Aids",
    description:
      "Use **progress indicators**, **checklists**, or **step-by-step flows** when relevant. Let users **collapse or expand content** (like accordions). Provide clear CTAs (Call-to-Action) with one main goal per page.",
  },
  {
    title: "Accessible, Soothing Design",
    description:
      " Gentle color palette with **high contrast** options for readability. Dyslexia-friendly fonts or defaults like **sans-serif** (e.g., Inter, Arial).Font size should be legible (16px+ body text).",
  },
  {
    title: "Customizability (if possible)**",
    description:
      "Let users toggle **dark/light mode**, **font size**, or **reduced motion**. Give control over how much information is shown at once. So when you say you offer custom digital artistry, you're saying: “I don’t just build websites—I co-create digital experiences that feel like an extension of your creative work",
  },
];
---

<div id="how-it-works-wrapper" class="">
  <!-- <div class="bg-">
    <CenterPageBanner
      BannerTitle="Main Goals"
      paragraph="All websites are built with”:"
    /> -->
</div>

<div id="how-it-works-container" class="bg- mt-5 2xl:px-[150px] pt-5 px-5">
  <div
    id="how-it-works-grid"
    class="grid 2xl:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 gap-5"
  >
    {
      items.map((item) => (
        <div
          id="sq-wrapper"
          class="flex justify-center bg-teal text-parchment sq-styles "
        >
          <div id="sq-container" class="p-3 w-full bg-">
            <p class="text-md  ">{item.description}</p>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold flex justify-end pt-5">
              {item.title}
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>
</div>
